// Tic Tac Toe Game 

A basic two-player Tic Tac Toe game built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

// Features
- Two-player turn-based gameplay
- Win and draw detection
- Game reset button
- Simple UI with responsive layout

// Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

// How to Run
1. Download or clone the repository
2. Open index.html in any browser
3. Start playing!

